{"tid":1568911,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"睇完連登，發現今時今日已經好少人講「兄弟爬山各自努力」","createTime":"2019-09-14T12:16:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T15:43:50.000Z","uid":151525,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"93babe047ad6571954159cd85a2ac89768606af1","tid":1568911,"uid":151525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:16:49.000Z","msg":"唔係講好不割不分不篤灰? <br />\n有人堅持著黑衫 有人認為要著藍衫<br />\n有人堅持勇武 有人認為唔可以打死人<br />\n有人堅持和理非 有人認為和理非都要升級<br />\n<br />\n香港始終同烏克蘭唔同<br />\n人地經濟一窮二白 可以Winter on Fire 香港人仍然有三餐溫飽 霎時要全民轉型 除非樓價大跌九成 <br />\n人地背靠歐盟北約 可以抗衡俄佬 香港人背後 美英澳加日台 全部各有政經盤算 14億人市場始終對佢地好吸引<br />\n<br />\n但經歷過今次Summer on Fire 香港即使唔係100%人醒覺 都有一半 呢一半醒覺嘅人 識唱願榮光歸香港嘅人 將來會令到中共好頭痕 當下keep住令中共頭痕嘅方法 就係<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不分化 不割蓆</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"69e84a4c645c5a97596c29e4f9c59e61b6b43da3","tid":1568911,"uid":151525,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:17:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>兄弟爬山各自努力</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"7f7ee6c2b200238dc843cc919424cc0c438200bd","tid":1568911,"uid":165028,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:18:23.000Z","msg":"歐盟受ukraine玩咩？<br />\n樓主做下research先啦"},{"pid":"5ed22e9ed5c33aec3376ab034b0c6bf5655480a3","tid":1568911,"uid":71713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:19:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f60b1a0ce6326430115502f061fdfd4a49f3294f","tid":1568911,"uid":201816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:20:02.000Z","msg":"兄弟爬山 天日一齊出嚟啦好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好唔記得915啊<br />\n大家快D幫手推上熱門啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1568633\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1568633</a>"},{"pid":"5fee5ca21c9b8e4809b133a7ce3c9616618741ad","tid":1568911,"uid":151525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"qu